General Information

2500mg Collagen per serving for that glow from within.

BEAUTY BEGINS WITHIN
It's time you turn the way you think about beauty upside down, or perhaps inside out (see what we did there). Collagen is one of the key building blocks of our skin. However, as the years go buy our body's natural production of Collagen reduces and we start to see those dreaded signs of ageing. 

WHY CHEW SUP?
Chew your supplements with SUP's delish gummies. Replenish your Collagen supplies with 2500mg of Collagen for that everyday glow. SUP helps:
-2500mg Collagen per serve
-Nourish the skin
-Boost your Collagen supplies
-Delicious way to get your Collagen CHEWSUP

Size: 40 Gummies

KEY FEATURES

• 2500mg Collagen per serve
• Nourish the skin
• Boost your Collagen supplies
• Delicious way to get your Collagen

Warnings

Excess consumption may have laxative effect. CONTAINS GLUTEN FROM WHEAT. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Reseal immediately after use.

Sweetener (malitol, sorbitol), Collagen hydrolysed, Gelling agent (gelatine), Water, Bulking agent (wheat starch), Acidity regulator (331, 330), Natural Flavour, Glazing agent (coconut oil, carnauba wax), Colour (160d).

Directions

Adults
Take 3 gummies daily
